and we'll skip those couple of verses,

00:32:24.639 --> 00:32:25.719
but look at verse number six

00:32:25.719 --> 00:32:28.559
and see again the heart of Esther.

00:32:28.559 --> 00:32:32.359
For how can I endure to see the evil

00:32:32.359 --> 00:32:36.579
that shall come unto my people?

00:32:36.579 --> 00:32:41.119
Or how can I endure to see the destruction of my kindred?

00:32:42.599 --> 00:32:47.039
Esther was moved by what she knew to be true.

00:32:47.959 --> 00:32:49.759
There was a decree that was written

00:32:50.719 --> 00:32:52.599
and had there not been a counter decree,

00:32:52.599 --> 00:32:54.319
all the Jews would have been killed on that day.

00:32:54.319 --> 00:32:56.399
That was the law that was written.

00:33:01.719 --> 00:33:06.719
God worked, God moved, but Esther,

00:33:09.159 --> 00:33:12.879
she besought the king with tears.

00:33:12.879 --> 00:33:15.439
And she says, how can I endure to see the evil

00:33:15.479 --> 00:33:17.719
that shall come unto my people?

00:33:17.719 --> 00:33:21.479
Or how can I endure to see the destruction of my kindred?

00:33:22.439 --> 00:33:24.219
When we study prophecy,

00:33:26.359 --> 00:33:29.279
I'm so thankful that Revelation four and five

00:33:29.279 --> 00:33:32.319
is a picture, a scene in the throne room of heaven

00:33:32.319 --> 00:33:35.559
and oh, what glory it's gonna be to be there one day,

00:33:35.559 --> 00:33:37.919
to see my savior face to face.

00:33:39.319 --> 00:33:42.359
But understand this evening that there are people

00:33:42.359 --> 00:33:45.339
that you know and that I know that are not saved.

00:33:46.919 --> 00:33:48.839
That when the rapture of the church takes place,

00:33:48.839 --> 00:33:51.279
they're going to be left behind

00:33:51.279 --> 00:33:53.039
and they're gonna suffer greatly.

00:33:53.039 --> 00:33:54.599
Many of them will die.

00:33:55.479 --> 00:33:56.799
In the first of these seals,

00:33:56.799 --> 00:33:59.559
I mean, we don't know the exact numbers

00:33:59.559 --> 00:34:02.959
because we don't know what the population of the earth

00:34:02.959 --> 00:34:05.399
will be at the moment of the start of the tribulation.

00:34:05.399 --> 00:34:06.859
We don't know the number of Christians

00:34:06.859 --> 00:34:08.799
that will be raptured and so on and so forth.

00:34:08.799 --> 00:34:11.279
But what I'm saying to you is that potentially

00:34:11.319 --> 00:34:13.639
billions of people will die.

00:34:15.799 --> 00:34:18.239
And if billions of people die without Christ,

00:34:18.239 --> 00:34:21.859
that means eventually they'll stand at the second judgment,

00:34:21.859 --> 00:34:26.159
that great white throne judgment, that second death.

00:34:27.239 --> 00:34:30.039
The Bible says that they shall be cast in a lake of fire.

00:34:30.919 --> 00:34:32.919
This is the second death.

00:34:32.919 --> 00:34:35.119
What I'm simply saying this evening is that

00:34:35.119 --> 00:34:37.759
when we look at the book of Revelation

00:34:37.759 --> 00:34:39.359
and I dealt with it a little bit last week

00:34:39.359 --> 00:34:41.799
and the Lord's just stirring my heart

00:34:41.799 --> 00:34:44.759
because yes, I wanna study the book of Revelation,

00:34:44.759 --> 00:34:46.639
understand prophecy and be able to,

00:34:46.639 --> 00:34:49.279
yes, people have questions and so on and so forth.

00:34:49.279 --> 00:34:50.999
But instead of getting into a room

00:34:50.999 --> 00:34:53.519
and debating with a bunch of people about prophecy

00:34:53.519 --> 00:34:55.439
and about all of these types of things,

00:34:55.439 --> 00:34:57.839
listen, we got work to do.

00:34:57.839 --> 00:34:59.099
People are dying.

00:35:00.239 --> 00:35:05.139
And listen, when the clock starts again for that 70th week,

00:35:06.139 --> 00:35:11.139
judgment, the Antichrist revealed,

00:35:12.499 --> 00:35:15.779
war, great famine, the desperation.

00:35:15.779 --> 00:35:19.159
Yes, it's divine judgment, but it results in desperation.

00:35:20.179 --> 00:35:21.439
How does it affect us?

00:35:21.439 --> 00:35:23.459
We see how it affected Esther

00:35:23.459 --> 00:35:26.619
with regard to that writing of Haman.

00:35:26.619 --> 00:35:29.219
She besought the king with tears.

00:35:29.219 --> 00:35:33.539
She said, how can I endure to see this?

00:35:33.539 --> 00:35:36.459
And sometimes as believers,

00:35:36.459 --> 00:35:39.779
we get so caught up with things going on in this world

00:35:40.659 --> 00:35:43.939
that we just go right past people

00:35:43.939 --> 00:35:45.619
and don't even give two thoughts

00:35:45.619 --> 00:35:47.799
about the fact that they need Jesus.

00:35:49.659 --> 00:35:50.979
You understand what I'm saying?

00:35:50.979 --> 00:35:52.659
I'm guilty of it as well.

00:35:53.639 --> 00:35:56.739
If we're all honest and evaluate ourselves, we're guilty.

00:35:58.659 --> 00:36:01.619
Give me a passion for souls, dear Lord.

00:36:02.619 --> 00:36:05.219
A passion, why?

00:36:05.219 --> 00:36:06.419
Because people are gonna die

00:36:06.419 --> 00:36:09.179
and spend eternity in the lake of fire.

00:36:09.179 --> 00:36:11.579
And I know we're not in Revelation chapter 20 yet.

00:36:11.579 --> 00:36:13.459
We'll get there in months,

00:36:13.459 --> 00:36:16.159
but we begin to just look at even

00:36:16.159 --> 00:36:17.799
the start of the tribulation.

00:36:19.019 --> 00:36:20.699
And I wonder this evening,

00:36:20.699 --> 00:36:22.379
listen, I don't preach these messages

00:36:22.379 --> 00:36:24.479
just so we can try to win an argument

00:36:24.479 --> 00:36:27.059
with somebody about eschatology.

00:36:27.059 --> 00:36:28.779
It's not the point.

00:36:28.779 --> 00:36:29.859
It's not the point.

00:36:29.859 --> 00:36:31.579
Someone asked me a question this morning after church.

00:36:31.579 --> 00:36:33.679
I'm like, look, man, if you don't believe it, it's fine.

00:36:33.679 --> 00:36:35.339
It's not like a doctrinal issue.

00:36:36.339 --> 00:36:37.859
It's okay.

00:36:37.859 --> 00:36:40.179
I don't say that to say that I'm interested in compromise

00:36:40.179 --> 00:36:41.019
and all that sort of thing,

00:36:41.019 --> 00:36:43.439
but there's some things that just aren't worth

00:36:43.439 --> 00:36:46.699
even talking about or fighting about for sure.

00:36:48.339 --> 00:36:49.659
Because they become distractions

00:36:49.659 --> 00:36:51.839
from really what the main thing is.

00:36:52.899 --> 00:36:55.499
I'm thankful that God gave us the record of the seals

00:36:55.499 --> 00:36:57.019
and we can read and we can understand

00:36:57.019 --> 00:36:58.499
and we can see what's coming.

00:36:58.539 --> 00:37:02.099
And we can understand that that famine is divine judgment.

00:37:02.099 --> 00:37:03.419
We can understand that it leaves,

00:37:03.419 --> 00:37:05.659
it results in desperation.

00:37:07.179 --> 00:37:08.939
Man, who do I know and who do you know

00:37:08.939 --> 00:37:11.739
that's gonna suffer potentially through that

00:37:11.739 --> 00:37:13.939
because we're not telling them about Jesus?

00:37:15.259 --> 00:37:17.179
Oh, that God would stir us up.

00:37:18.019 --> 00:37:19.719
That God would do a work in our hearts

00:37:19.719 --> 00:37:23.339
to give us a passion for souls.

00:37:23.339 --> 00:37:25.059
Because people are dying.

00:37:25.059 --> 00:37:27.659
I think it's my father-in-law's favorite song.

00:37:27.699 --> 00:37:28.539
Some of you might know,

00:37:28.539 --> 00:37:30.559
it's not a song that we sing really.

00:37:30.559 --> 00:37:32.339
People need the Lord.

00:37:32.339 --> 00:37:33.499
I don't know if you ever heard that song.

00:37:33.499 --> 00:37:35.019
It's his favorite song, right?

00:37:35.019 --> 00:37:36.379
People need the Lord.

00:37:36.379 --> 00:37:37.619
They do.

00:37:37.619 --> 00:37:39.419
They need Jesus.

00:37:39.419 --> 00:37:40.239
And guess what?

00:37:40.239 --> 00:37:42.659
Just like someone had to tell you about Jesus,

00:37:42.659 --> 00:37:46.339
they need someone to tell them about Jesus.

00:37:46.339 --> 00:37:47.179
Amen?

00:37:47.179 --> 00:37:47.999
Let's pray.

00:37:47.999 --> 00:37:49.419
Father, we love you.

00:37:49.419 --> 00:37:51.379
Thank you for loving us.

00:37:51.379 --> 00:37:52.699
Thank you for the word of God.

00:37:52.699 --> 00:37:56.099
Thank you that you've given to us the truth

00:37:56.179 --> 00:37:58.419
that we can know the truth.

00:37:58.419 --> 00:38:03.419
And God, I pray that the truth would stir us.

00:38:05.099 --> 00:38:07.219
Think of Paul when he was there in Athens

00:38:07.219 --> 00:38:11.379
and he saw a city that was wholly given to idolatry

00:38:11.379 --> 00:38:13.819
and how his spirit was stirred within him.

00:38:15.059 --> 00:38:16.299
And he went into that place

00:38:16.299 --> 00:38:17.859
and he preached unto them Jesus.

00:38:17.859 --> 00:38:21.259
He said, I saw this altar to the unknown God.

00:38:21.259 --> 00:38:22.739
Him declare I unto you.

00:38:22.739 --> 00:38:27.739
Oh God, would you help us to be good, faithful ambassadors,

00:38:29.059 --> 00:38:30.739
to be your witnesses, to go forth

00:38:30.739 --> 00:38:32.939
and preach the gospel to every creature.

00:38:34.019 --> 00:38:38.739
We believe the coming of the Lord draweth nigh.

00:38:38.739 --> 00:38:41.419
We do not in any way try to set dates or timelines,

00:38:41.419 --> 00:38:44.699
but Lord, I pray you'd help us to be motivated,

00:38:46.619 --> 00:38:48.419
to live a life that pleases you,

00:38:49.539 --> 00:38:51.179
and that you'd give us the opportunity

00:38:51.179 --> 00:38:53.379
to bring as many people to heaven with us

00:38:53.379 --> 00:38:55.139
as we possibly can.

00:38:55.139 --> 00:38:57.939
Thank you that the gospel is the power of God unto salvation.

00:38:57.939 --> 00:38:59.899
Thank you that you still save sinners.

00:39:00.979 --> 00:39:03.619
Use us, God, for your glory and we'll thank you for it.

00:39:03.619 --> 00:39:04.859
In Christ's name we pray.

